Reporting back after playing for a few hrs, and I have to say I'm very dissapointed with this series. The graphics are seriously lacking compared to the newer games such as Gears 3 and MW3. Gameplay is very sloppy also.  Capcom really dropped the ball on this one, as I have been anticipating to play this game for a while. Rather we get a game that looks like a souped up Saints Row "2". I hope they dont continue this path with RE6.

honestly, i not surprise why graphic and story mode are so plain like this.

cause this game aim to sell as mmo co-op game. that why they reduce graphic to maintain frame rate and bandwidth for playing online.

in another word, this game not worth for play off line as single player mode.  

better wait to see what version pc look like in the next 2 months.
